-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-08/humala-to-boost-coca-eradication-in-peru-el-comercio-says.html
Peruvian President Ollanta Humala
plans to eradicate illegal coca crops with the aid of satellite
technology, El Comercio  reported , citing comments by Defense
Minister Daniel Mora.  The government will encourage the cultivation of
alternative crops and halt the supply of chemicals to drug-
producing areas, Mora said in an interview posted on the Lima-
